FBIS4-57803 "drlat101_m_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 Brazil PPR Names Candidates for Presidential Ticket PPR Names Candidates for Presidential Ticket PY2505024594 Sao Paulo AGENCIA ESTADO in Portuguese 2207 GMT 24 May 94 PY2505024594 Sao Paulo AGENCIA ESTADO Portuguese BFN [Report by Diana Fernandes] [Excerpt] Brasilia, 24 May (AE) -- The Progressive Renewal Party [PPR] convention today approved the nomination of Senator Esperidiao Amin of Santa Catarina State and former Sao Luiz Mayor Gardenia Goncalves as candidates for president and vice president on the PPR ticket. [passage omitted]
